      boolean startSession()
      Reads the user Atm card gets the id and the pin and then if there is a matching user sets the current Atm user to the matching user on success otherwise the Atm reports an error and continues to ask the user for id and pin Note: IF there is already a current user when this is called, then handle as a continuation of the currentSession

    • Method Detail

      • startSession

        public boolean startSession()
        Reads the user Atm card gets the id and the pin and then if there is a matching user sets the current Atm user to the matching user on success otherwise the Atm reports an error and continues to ask the user for id and pin Note: IF there is already a current user when this is called, then handle as a continuation of the currentSession
        Returns:
        true if session starts; false if user wants to exit

      • endSession

        Transaction Type
